import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';

function AddLocPage() {
  return (
    <Form>
        <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
        <option>위치 타입 선택</option>
        <option value="1">One</option>
        <option value="2">Two</option>
        <option value="3">Three</option>
        </Form.Select>

        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicPassword">
            <Form.Label>위치명</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="위치명입력" />
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicPassword">
            <Form.Label>위치 포인트</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="위치 포인트 입력" />
        </Form.Group>
        <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formBasicPassword">
            <Form.Label>위치 포인트</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="file" placeholder="위치 포인트 입력" />
        </Form.Group>
        
        <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
            Submit
        </Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default AddLocPage;
